name: identifier
label: Identifier
description: A unique proper name or character sequence that identifies this particular metabolomics material processing. (NCIT:C132299 )

name: belongstomaterials
label: Belongs to materials
description: Reference to the source material from which this sample was prepared. (NCIT:C93400, NCIT:C25683 )

name: processingtype
label: Processing type
description: A planned process which results in physical changes in a specified input material. (OBI:0000094 )

name: sampleextraction
label: Sample extraction
description: The transfer of a solute from a liquid phase to another immiscible or partially-miscible liquid phase in contact with it. (CHMO:0001577 )

name: filterused
label: Filter used
description: The filter used in separating of suspended solids from a liquid or gas, usually by forcing a carrier gas or liquid through a porous medium. (CHMO:0001640 )

name: passingrate
label: Passing rate
description: The volume of carrier gas passing through a chromatography column in unit time. (CHMO:0002751 )

name: specartridge
label: SPE cartridge
description: A sample preparation technique using a solid adsorbent contained most commonly in a cartridge device, or on a disk to adsorb select species from solution. (OMIT:0025161 )

name: washingprotocol
label: Washing protocol
description: Washing is a process by which a material entity acting as contaminant (e.g. excess staining reagent) is removed by application of one or more cycles of solution in flow. (OBI:0302888 )
